race.comment: LAURIE'S RUPEE (3) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at Maitland in a handy 22.48 beating Tralee Enzo. Expected to measure up again. OFFENBACH (2) boasts a strong record this journey here with five wins and two minors from 12 tries. Below best last time at this track (23.57) in a NG, finishing a 13 length fifth. Can feature in the finish. RARE OBSIDIAN (5) goes very well here starting 15 times for seven wins and six minors. Hit the frame latest (22.96) when second at this track in a Grade 4/5. Suited here and expected to run well. SMART PANAMA (1) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.
